Posts.Content: Hi there I had a similar thing after my first round of FEC. I had a runny nose and wheezy cough with some mucous on my chest..... My temp wasn't up so I just waited and about 3 days later it went. I just put it down to one of the many weird but not too bad side effects....xxxxx
